## **১. প্রাথমিক ধাপ (Prerequisites)**

1. Windows Server 2016/2019/2022
2. Admin Privileges
3. Internet Access for downloading monitoring agents
4. Backup storage drive (ex: `E:`)
5. Company Email Domain (ex: `@company.com`) with SMTP access
