## **৩. Backup + Daily Validation**

### **Automated Backup**

```powershell
# Daily full backup at 2 AM
$action = New-ScheduledTaskAction -Execute "wbadmin" -Argument "start backup -backupTarget:E: -include:C: -allCritical -quiet"
$trigger = New-ScheduledTaskTrigger -Daily -At 2am
Register-ScheduledTask -Action $action -Trigger $trigger -TaskName "DailyFullBackup"
```

### **Backup Validation Script**

```powershell
$backupVersions = wbadmin get versions
if ($backupVersions) {
    Write-Host "Backup exists: OK"
} else {
    Send-MailMessage -From "admin@company.com" -To "itadmin@company.com" -Subject "Backup Failed" -Body "Daily backup not found!" -SmtpServer "smtp.company.com"
}
```

* এই স্ক্রিপ্ট **Scheduled Task** হিসেবে দিন শেষে চালান।

