## **৪. Email Alerts Setup (Company Domain)**

1. Enable PowerShell SMTP email alerts:

```powershell
$SMTPServer = "smtp.company.com"
$From = "admin@company.com"
$To = "itadmin@company.com"
$Subject = "Server Alert"
$Body = "CPU > 85% on Server $(hostname) at $(Get-Date)"
Send-MailMessage -From $From -To $To -Subject $Subject -Body $Body -SmtpServer $SMTPServer -Port 587 -Credential (Get-Credential)
```

* `Get-Credential`-এ admin email credentials দিন।
* Alerts include: CPU spikes, Disk < 10%, Backup failure, Failed logons, etc.

