## **৬. Firewall & Network Control**

```powershell
# Block SMB
New-NetFirewallRule -DisplayName "Block SMB" -Direction Inbound -LocalPort 445 -Protocol TCP -Action Block

# Allow RDP only from IT subnet
New-NetFirewallRule -DisplayName "Allow RDP IT" -Direction Inbound -LocalPort 3389 -RemoteAddress "192.168.10.0/24" -Action Allow
```

* VLAN/subnet separation for Finance, HR, IT.
* Monitoring alerts for suspicious connections via Zabbix/Nagios.

